Eccellente vestibilità: ogni portapacchi laterale Hepco & Becker Lock-it è perfettamente compatibile con il rispettivo tipo di moto. In questo modo si ottiene una precisione molto elevata del supporto sulla moto. Realizzato in tubo di acciaio e parti laser realizzate su misura, che vengono ulteriormente rinforzate nei punti più sollecitati. La qualità dei supporti Lock-it è stata confermata in passato da riviste specializzate.

I supporti si montano e smontano in pochi secondi. Basta allentare le viti Lock-it installate con un quarto di giro e si possono rimuovere le parti laterali verso il retro o verso il lato. Come protezione antifurto è possibile proteggere il supporto dalle dita lunghe con le nostre viti bloccabili Lock-it (codice articolo: 151050).
Tutte le valigie sono completate da una chiusura rapida sul supporto. Per questo è necessario l'adattatore in alluminio (numero articolo 700114) che normalmente sono inclusi nella valigetta. Gli adattatori in alluminio vengono avvitati a destra e a sinistra sul supporto e offrono quindi una possibilità di fissaggio per i lucchetti della valigia.

Per tutte le valigie laterali Hepco & Becker
Struttura stabile.
Rimovibile rapidamente, rimangono solo piccole linguette poco appariscenti sulla moto.
Rivestimento di alta qualità.
Di solito facile montaggio, si prega di seguire le istruzioni di montaggio incluse (lingua italiana non garantita).

desc2:
Il problema del fissaggio dei bagagli agli agli sportivi è noto a tutti. Hepco & Becker ha anche una soluzione adeguata: la pista sportiva ancorata al posto del sedile passeggero nel supporto originale e si apre tramite chiave di accensione del veicolo. Le possibilità di fissaggio per le cinghie offrono una presa sicura a tutti i bagagli. Espandibile con una estensione, adatto anche per grandi rotoli di valigia.
L'aspetto della Sportracks è uguale a un coprisedile passeggero ed è grazie al suo design un ulteriore punto di attrazione. Il divertimento di guida rimane inalterato grazie al fissaggio sicuro del bagaglio, direttamente dietro il conducente e non pregiudica in alcun modo il comportamento della macchina.

Verniciatura a polvere di alta qualità.
Montaggio semplice.
Contenuto della confezione: piastra sportiva, controstaffa di fissaggio, materiale di montaggio, istruzioni di montaggio (lingua italiana non garantita).
Carico consigliato: 5 kg (si prega di leggere le indicazioni specifiche del veicolo, nonché le istruzioni di montaggio e le indicazioni del produttore di moto).
Adatto solo in combinazione con i nostri bauletti da viaggio 30/40/50 nella versione universale con piastra in plastica. I normali bauletti Hepco & Becker non sono adatti.
Può essere combinato con la nostra borsa sportiva per il bagagliaio Street, o con la borsa da serbatoio Daypack.
Non è necessaria l'omologazione o la registrazione.
Si prega di osservare le istruzioni di montaggio riportate (lingua italiana non garantita).

desc2: The original history of the Suntour company dates back to the 10s of the 20th century: Initially started as a manufacturer of crowns, transmission components etc. for bicycles, the company has increasingly focused on additional components, especially in the field of gearboxes. Some important innovations can be traced back to Suntour: For example, the current rasterization of switching steps. Since the 1990s, the Japanese manufacturer has expanded its portfolio with suspension forks, shock absorbers and power systems for e-bikes, among others. As a manufacturer of original equipment for numerous bicycle brands, Suntour occupies an important position among component manufacturers alongside Shimano and SRAM.

Excellent fit – every Hepco & Becker lock-it side carrier is precisely matched to the respective motorcycle type. This results in a very high fit of the carrier on the motorcycle. Made from tubular steel and custom-made laser parts, which are reinforced once again in heavily stressed areas. The quality of the lock-it straps has been confirmed several times in specialist magazines.

The straps can be mounted and removed in seconds. You only need to loosen the attached lock-it screws with a quarter turn and you can take the side parts back or to the side. As a theft protection, you can optionally protect the carrier with our lockable lock-it screws from long fingers (item number: 151050).
All cases are closed with a quick release fastener on the strap. For this purpose, you need the aluminium adaptor (item number 700114) which are usually included in the case. The aluminium adaptors are screwed on the right and left side of the carrier and then offer a mounting option for the locking locks of the case.

title: Sena 10U Motorcycle Bluetooth Communication System with Handlebar Remote for Arai Full-Face Helmets
description:
About this item
Invisible beauty with a custom design
Simple and safe operation via the low-power Bluetooth Handlebar Remote

desc2:
The Sena 10U for Arai Full Face Helmet is a Bluetooth communication system for bikes with Handlebar Remote designed for the Arai Integral helmet.

With Bluetooth 4.0 technology, the 10U is an invisible beauty with a custom design that fits into the helmet's ear pockets allowing for easy, versatile wear. The 10U includes four-way intercom conversations up to 1 mile with Universal Intercom and Group Intercom technology, as well as intuitive voice instructions. Using innovative technology, the 10U offers safe and easy operations with a remote control, as well as a two-button control pad for emergency control.

If it's not enough to hit the road with ease and powerful connectivity, other key features include music sharing, built-in FM radio tuner, Advanced Noise Control, external wired antenna for the helmet with installation, up to 10 hours of talk time, and a smartphone app for iPhone and Android, all with upgradeable firmware.

desc2: If you are looking for a high-quality telescope with a professional design that is easy to set up and use, the Celestron AstroMaster 102AZ Series is your best choice. The AstroMaster 102AZ refractor telescope can be used by adults and children at the same time, is powerful and easy to use, and is designed with a lightweight frame and fully coated optics. Our Celestron telescope has a fully coated primary mirror. It also features an AstroMaster manual altazimuth mount, which includes a panoramic handle that allows precision adjustments for easy tracking of celestial objects moving across the night sky. The two eyepieces combine with the 102mm aperture optics to generate amazing magnification. The 20mm eyepiece offers 33x magnification, while the 10mm eyepiece offers up to 66x close views. This allows you to focus distant objects with incredible sharpness. We designed the AstroMaster telescope series for kids to enjoy exploring space with adult supervision. Its superior materials offer clear, crisp images of Saturn, Jupiter and the Moon, as well as space objects such as galaxies or nebulae. You can also use this telescope to view terrestrial objects during the day. The telescope sets up quickly without any tools. The kit includes a sturdy pre-assembled tripod with 1.25" steel tube legs, which offer stability and allow hours of safe use. Additionally, download BONUS Starry Night Basic Edition astronomical software to perform interactive simulations in the sky, with a database of 36,000 objects and printable celestial maps. It's the best way to learn about the night sky, download printable celestial maps, investigate thousands of celestial bodies, and plan your next observation session. Shop with peace of mind the #1 telescope brand in the world, based in California since 1960. You will also receive a two-year warranty and unlimited access to technical support from our team of US experts.

title: Hepco & Becker C-Bow sidecarrier for Moto Guzzi V 7 II Classic from 2015 | 630545 00 01
desc2:
Todos los bolsillos laterales de Hepco & Becker o de piel o maletas con grabación de sonido en C se pueden fijar a la moto con la ayuda de soportes específicos del modelo. El discreto y elegante diseño encaja perfectamente en la línea general del vehículo. Por supuesto, una distancia de seguridad suficiente de los bolsillos al extremo del tubo de escape caliente. Gracias a la tecnología C-Bow, las bolsas se colocan rápida y fácilmente en el soporte C-Bow con un solo clic y se fijan mediante una llave. Las bolsas están firmemente conectadas a la moto y permanecen en posición incluso con la carga. Los intermitentes permanecen en la posición original. Tenga en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje y las indicaciones específicas del modelo.

Tirantes sólidos para la inclusión de Hepco & Becker C-Bow bolsillos laterales y maletas.
Revestimiento de calidad.
Ajuste perfecto, diseño específico del modelo de la línea de la moto.
Maletín rígido normal Hepco & Becker como el Junior o Journey.
El maletín Krauser K-Wing no se ajusta al soporte C-Bow.
El portador está diseñado de forma mucho más discreta que un portaequipajes lateral normal y por lo tanto no es adecuado para grandes cargas.
Carga recomendada: 5 kg por bolsa (por favor, tenga en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje, indicaciones específicas del vehículo, así como datos del fabricante de la motocicleta).
Se pueden combinar sin problemas con portaequipajes, barras de sisal o solares (ten en cuenta las instrucciones de instalación o las indicaciones específicas del vehículo).
Los ampliaciones del puente del equipaje pueden limitar el montaje de los bolsillos en el soporte.
Portaequipajes no necesita ABE o registro en los papeles.

About this item
LSL - Clutch lever L29
Black/Red
desc2:
Long clutch lever.
The correct lever length, ergonomic shape and tailor-made manufacturing are all requirements for optimal dosing of brake and clutch forces. Economical grip for all hand sizes, lever position is adjustable in 6 positions. The bracket of the adjustment clips is ball bearing. The adjustment lever is particularly operable with its excellent knob and thus allows adjustment even during travel. The storage of the lever mechanism is carried out in long-life brass bushings. A generous opening at the end of the lever serves as a breaking point and thus allows sufficient function of the lever after a fall.
The standard version of the LSL lever is made for full hand access. The short version is ideal for braking systems that work well and offers space for the handle with three fingers. Both versions are delivered with ABE.

Para todos los portaequipajes laterales Hepco & Becker

Tutti conoscono il problema del fissaggio del bagaglio ai supersportivi. Hepco & Becker ha anche una soluzione appropriata: la bici sportiva, che viene ancorata al posto del sedile passeggero nella registrazione originale e si apre con la chiave di accensione del veicolo. Le possibilità di fissaggio complete per le cinghie offrono una presa sicura per tutti i bagagli. Espandibile con un estensore adatto anche per grandi ruote bagagli.
L'aspetto della sella sportiva assomiglia a un coprisedile passeggero e grazie al suo design è un ulteriore highlight ottico. Il divertimento di guida rimane inalterato grazie al fissaggio sicuro del bagaglio direttamente dietro il conducente e non compromette in alcun modo il comportamento di guida della macchina.

Verniciatura a polvere di alta qualità.
Montaggio semplice.
Contenuto della confezione: piastra sportiva, supporto di fissaggio, materiale di montaggio, istruzioni di montaggio (lingua italiana non garantita).
Carico consigliato: 5 kg (si prega di leggere le istruzioni specifiche per il veicolo, nonché le istruzioni di montaggio e le indicazioni del produttore di moto).
Adatto solo in combinazione con i nostri bauletto Journey 30/40/50 nella versione universale con piastra in plastica. Le normali custodie Hepco & Becker non si adattano perfettamente!
Può essere combinato con la nostra borsa da sella Sportrack Street, o con lo zaino Daypack.
Non è necessaria l'omologazione o la registrazione.
Si prega di leggere attentamente le istruzioni di montaggio (lingua italiana non garantita).

title: Hepco & Becker Modelspecific rear enlargement for Triumph Tiger 1050 Sport from 2013 | 8007523 00 01
description:
Sturdy aluminium plate for widening almost all luggage bridges when you don't want to carry a top case, but loose luggage. Thanks to the raised edges and the additional breakpoints, the widening is ideal for safely transporting larger luggage rolls, travel bags, tents, duffel bags, etc. Construction made of aluminium with high strength and high-quality look. Mounting options for straps. Dimensions: long width: 48 cm. Short width: 39 cm. Depth: 28 cm. Thickness: 4 mm
Not suitable for top case mounting. Recommended load: 5 kg. Includes mounting material and instructions (English language not guaranteed). High-quality plastic coating
› See more product details

title: Hepco & Becker C-Bow sidecarrier for Ducati Monster 1100 evo | 6307502 00 01
desc2:
All Hepco & Becker side leather bags or cases with C-Bow mount can be attached to the motorcycle with the help of model-specific C-Bow straps. The discreet and elegant design fits perfectly into the overall line of the vehicle. A sufficient safety distance between the bags and the hot end pot of the exhaust is of course. Thanks to the C-Bow technology, the matching bags are quickly and easily attached to the C-Bow carrier with just one click, and are protected against theft and locked securely by key. The bags are firmly connected to the motorcycle and remain in position even when loaded The indicators usually remain in their original position. Please refer to the detailed assembly instructions and model-specific instructions.

Solid straps for attaching Hepco & Becker C-ow side pockets and suitcases
High-quality coating
Precisely fitting, model-specific design adapted to the lines of the motorcycle
Normal Hepco & Becker hard case as the junior or journey does not fit.
Krauser K-Wing case does not fit on the C-Bow carrier!
The carrier is much more discreet than a normal side carrier and therefore not suitable for large loads.
Recommended load: 5 kg per bag (please refer to the assembly instructions, vehicle-specific instructions, as well as motorcycle manufacturer specifications).
Can be combined with top case carriers, sissy bars, or solo packs (please refer to the installation instructions or the vehicle-specific instructions).
Luggage bridge wideners can limit bag mounting on the carrier.
Pannier rack does not require ABE or registration in the papers.

title: Hepco & Becker C-Bow sidecarrier for Yamaha FZ 8 | 6304532 00 01
desc2:
Todos los bolsillos laterales de Hepco & Becker o de piel o maletas con grabación de sonido en C se pueden fijar a la moto con la ayuda de soportes específicos del modelo. El discreto y elegante diseño encaja perfectamente en la línea general del vehículo. Por supuesto, una distancia de seguridad suficiente de los bolsillos al extremo del tubo de escape caliente. Gracias a la tecnología C-Bow, las bolsas se colocan rápida y fácilmente en el soporte C-Bow con un solo clic y se fijan mediante una llave. Las bolsas están firmemente conectadas a la moto y permanecen en posición incluso con la carga. Los intermitentes permanecen en la posición original. Tenga en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje y las indicaciones específicas del modelo.

Tirantes sólidos para la inclusión de Hepco & Becker C-Bow bolsillos laterales y maletas.
Revestimiento de calidad.
Ajuste perfecto, diseño específico del modelo de la línea de la moto.
Maletín rígido normal Hepco & Becker como el Junior o Journey.
El maletín Krauser K-Wing no se ajusta al soporte C-Bow.
El portador está diseñado de forma mucho más discreta que un portaequipajes lateral normal y por lo tanto no es adecuado para grandes cargas.
Carga recomendada: 5 kg por bolsa (por favor, tenga en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje, indicaciones específicas del vehículo, así como datos del fabricante de la motocicleta).
Se pueden combinar sin problemas con portaequipajes, barras de sisal o solares (ten en cuenta las instrucciones de instalación o las indicaciones específicas del vehículo).
Los ampliaciones del puente del equipaje pueden limitar el montaje de los bolsillos en el soporte.
Portaequipajes no necesita ABE o registro en los papeles.

title: Hepco & Becker Sportrack for Kawasaki Z 300 | 6702521 00 01
desc2:
Il problema del fissaggio dei bagagli agli agli sportivi è noto a tutti. Hepco & Becker ha anche una soluzione adeguata: la pista sportiva ancorata al posto del sedile passeggero nel supporto originale e si apre tramite chiave di accensione del veicolo. Le possibilità di fissaggio per le cinghie offrono una presa sicura a tutti i bagagli. Espandibile con una estensione, adatto anche per grandi rotoli di valigia.

Il divertimento di guida rimane inalterato grazie al fissaggio sicuro del bagaglio, direttamente dietro il conducente e non pregiudica in alcun modo il comportamento della macchina.

Non è necessaria l'omologazione o la registrazione.
Si prega di osservare le istruzioni di montaggio riportate (lingua italiana non garantita).

title: Hepco & Becker C-Bow sidecarrier - black for Suzuki GSX-S 750 from 2017 | 6303540 00 01
description:
About this item
Todos los bolsillos laterales, de cuero o maletas HEPCO & Becker con C-Bow se pueden fijar a la moto con la ayuda de los soportes C-Bow específicos para el modelo. El diseño discreto y elegante se adapta perfectamente a la línea general del vehículo. Una distancia de seguridad suficiente de los bolsillos para el tubo de escape caliente es evidente. Gracias a la tecnología C-Bow, los bolsillos correspondientes se colocan rápida y fácilmente en el soporte C-Bow y se bloquean con una llave
protegido y firmemente bloqueado. Las bolsas están firmemente conectadas a la moto y permanecen en su sitio incluso cuando está cargada. Los intermitentes suelen permanecer en la posición original. Ten en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje (idioma español no garantizado) y las indicaciones específicas del modelo. Sólido soporte para alojar los bolsillos laterales y maletines HEPCO & BECKER C-Bow, revestimiento de alta calidad, ajuste perfecto, construcción específica del modelo de la línea de la motocicleta, ajuste normal HEPCO & Becker rígido
Como los Junior o Journey no encajan. Las maletas K-Wing de Krauser no encajan en el soporte C-Bow. title: Hepco & Becker Sidecarrier Lock-it-black for Yamaha FZ 8 | 6504532 00 01
desc2:
Ajuste excelente: cada portaequipajes Hepco & Becker Lock-it se adapta exactamente a cada tipo de motocicleta. Esto resulta en una muy alta adaptación del soporte en la motocicleta. Fabricado en tubo de acero y piezas láser a medida, que se refuerza en zonas muy exigentes. La calidad de los soportes Lock-it ya ha sido confirmada en varias ocasiones en revistas especializadas.

Los tirantes se pueden montar y desmontar en cuestión de segundos. Solo hay que aflojar los tornillos Lock-it con un cuarto de vuelta y ya se pueden quitar los laterales hacia atrás o hacia el lado. Como protección antirrobo se puede proteger opcionalmente el soporte con nuestros tornillos Lock-it de los dedos largos (número de artículo: 151050).
Todas las maletas se cierran mediante un cierre rápido en el soporte. Para ello se necesita el adaptador de aluminio (número de artículo 700114) que normalmente está incluido en el maletín. Los adaptadores de aluminio se atornillan a la derecha y a la izquierda en el soporte y ofrecen una posibilidad de fijación para las cerraduras de sujeción del maletín.

Para todos los portaequipajes laterales Hepco & Becker
Estructura estable.
Fácil de desmontar, solo quedan discretas pequeñas pestañas en la motocicleta.
Revestimiento de calidad.
Por lo general es fácil de montar, ten en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje (idioma español no garantizado).

title: Hepco&Becker C-Bow Side Carrier Black for Yamaha MT - 03 Models 2016
desc2:
All Hepco & Becker side leather bags or cases with C-Bow mount can be attached to the motorcycle with the help of model-specific C-Bow straps. Thanks to the C-Bow technology, the matching bags are quickly and easily attached to the C-Bow carrier with just one click, and are protected against theft and locked securely by key. The bags are firmly connected to the motorcycle and remain in position even when loaded The indicators usually remain in their original position. Solid straps for attaching Hepco & Becker C-ow side pockets and suitcases
High-quality coating
Precisely fitting, model-specific design adapted to the lines of the motorcycle
Normal Hepco & Becker hard case as the junior or journey does not fit.
Krauser K-Wing case does not fit on the C-Bow carrier!
The carrier is much more discreet than a normal side carrier and therefore not suitable for large loads.

Can be combined with top case carriers, sissy bars, or solo packs (please refer to the installation instructions or the vehicle-specific instructions).
Luggage bridge wideners can limit bag mounting on the carrier.

title: Hepco & Becker Sportrack for Yamaha MT 125 ABS | 6704543 00 01
desc2:
Todos conocemos el problema de la fijación del equipaje en los superdeportistas. Hepco & Becker también tiene una solución adecuada: el track deportivo, que en lugar del asiento del pasajero se ancla en la toma original y se abre mediante la llave de encendido del vehículo. Las posibilidades de fijación para correas de equipaje proporcionan un agarre seguro a todas las piezas de equipaje. Ampliable con una ampliación también adecuado para grandes ruedas de equipaje.
El aspecto de la barra deportiva es similar a la cubierta del asiento del pasajero y por su diseño es un atractivo óptico adicional. La diversión de conducción se mantiene intacta gracias a la fijación segura del equipaje directamente detrás del conductor y no afecta en modo alguno al comportamiento de la máquina.

Revestimiento de polvo de alta calidad.
Fácil de montar.

Adecuado solo en combinación con nuestras fundas de Journey 30/40/50 en la versión universal con placa de plástico. Las fundas normales Hepco & Becker no encajan.
Se puede combinar con nuestra bolsa trasera Sportrack Street, o con la mochila de depósito Daypack.
No requiere certificado de aptitud técnica general (ABE) o registro de datos.
Se ruega tener en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje (idioma español no garantizado).

Todos los bolsillos laterales, de cuero o maletas HEPCO & Becker con C-Bow se pueden fijar a la moto con la ayuda de los soportes C-Bow específicos para el modelo. El diseño discreto y elegante se adapta perfectamente a la línea general del vehículo. Una distancia de seguridad suficiente de los bolsillos para el tubo de escape caliente es evidente. Gracias a la tecnología C-Bow, los bolsillos correspondientes se colocan rápida y fácilmente en el soporte C-Bow y se bloquean con una llave
protegido y firmemente bloqueado. Las bolsas están firmemente conectadas a la moto y permanecen en su sitio incluso cuando está cargada. Los intermitentes suelen permanecer en la posición original. Ten en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje (idioma español no garantizado) y las indicaciones específicas del modelo. Sólido soporte para alojar los bolsillos laterales y maletines HEPCO & BECKER C-Bow, revestimiento de alta calidad, ajuste perfecto, construcción específica del modelo de la línea de la motocicleta, ajuste normal HEPCO & Becker rígido
Como los Junior o Journey no encajan. Las maletas K-Wing de Krauser no encajan en el soporte C-Bow. El soporte es mucho más discreto que un portaequipajes lateral normal y, por lo tanto, no es adecuado para grandes cargas. Carga recomendada: 5 kg por bolsa (por favor ten en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje, las indicaciones específicas del vehículo y los datos del fabricante de motocicletas). Se puede combinar fácilmente con portaequipajes, barras de asiento o soloracks (ten en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje (idioma español no garantizado)
Indicaciones precisas). Las ampliaciones de puentes pueden limitar el montaje de la bolsa en el portaequipajes, no requieren ABE o registro en los documentos

title: Hepco & Becker C-Bow sidecarrier for Honda CB 1100 RS (2017-) | 6309502 00 01
desc2:
All Hepco & Becker side leather bags or cases with C-Bow mount can be attached to the motorcycle with the help of model-specific C-Bow straps. The discreet and elegant design fits perfectly into the overall line of the vehicle. A sufficient safety distance between the bags and the hot end pot of the exhaust is of course. Thanks to the C-Bow technology, the matching bags are quickly and easily attached to the C-Bow carrier with just one click, and are protected against theft and locked securely by key. Solid straps for attaching Hepco & Becker C-ow side pockets and suitcases
High-quality coating
Precisely fitting, model-specific design adapted to the lines of the motorcycle
Normal Hepco & Becker hard case as the junior or journey does not fit.
Krauser K-Wing case does not fit on the C-Bow carrier!
The carrier is much more discreet than a normal side carrier and therefore not suitable for large loads.
Recommended load: 5 kg per bag (please refer to the assembly instructions, vehicle-specific instructions, as well as motorcycle manufacturer specifications).
Can be combined with top case carriers, sissy bars, or solo packs (please refer to the installation instructions or the vehicle-specific instructions).
Luggage bridge wideners can limit bag mounting on the carrier.
Pannier rack does not require ABE or registration in the papers.

Portapacchi Bonneville Speedmaster a partire dall'anno di costruzione 2018
desc2:
I normali portapacchi laterali Hepco & Becker sono avvitati saldamente alla moto. Su questi supporti si adattano a tutte le normali custodie rigide Hepco & Becker. Le valigie vengono fissate al supporto mediante una chiusura rapida. Inoltre è necessario un adattatore in alluminio, che normalmente è incluso nella valigia. (Codice articolo: 700114). Questo adattatore in alluminio è avvitato posteriore a destra e a sinistra sul supporto e offre l'attacco per il lucchetto.
Le barre realizzate su misura per modello sono state sviluppate in modo solido e offrono una protezione efficace per le gambe del conducente o del passeggero anche in caso di caduta.
I portapacchi laterali di Hepco&Becker possono essere combinati senza problemi con un ponte per portapacchi o altri portapacchi posteriore della nostra casa. Si prega di leggere le istruzioni di montaggio (lingua italiana non garantita).

Struttura in tubo d'acciaio.
Avvitato saldamente alla moto.
Gli indicatori di direzione rimangono spesso nella posizione originale, ma a volte devono essere spostati (si prega di leggere le istruzioni di montaggio con il prodotto).
Carico consigliato: 10 kg per valigetta laterale (si prega di leggere le indicazioni specifiche del modello dei produttori di moto o le indicazioni sulle istruzioni di montaggio).
Per destra e sinistra con materiale di montaggio e istruzioni
Il portapacchi non necessita di omologazione o registrazione.

title: Hepco & Becker C-Bow sidecarrier for Kawasaki Z125 (2018-) | 6302536 00 01
desc2:
Todos los bolsillos laterales de Hepco & Becker o de piel o maletas con grabación de sonido en C se pueden fijar a la moto con la ayuda de soportes específicos del modelo. El discreto y elegante diseño encaja perfectamente en la línea general del vehículo. Por supuesto, una distancia de seguridad suficiente de los bolsillos al extremo del tubo de escape caliente. Gracias a la tecnología C-Bow, las bolsas se colocan rápida y fácilmente en el soporte C-Bow con un solo clic y se fijan mediante una llave. Las bolsas están firmemente conectadas a la moto y permanecen en posición incluso con la carga. Los intermitentes permanecen en la posición original. Tenga en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje y las indicaciones específicas del modelo.

Tirantes sólidos para la inclusión de Hepco & Becker C-Bow bolsillos laterales y maletas.
Revestimiento de calidad.
Ajuste perfecto, diseño específico del modelo de la línea de la moto.
Maletín rígido normal Hepco & Becker como el Junior o Journey.
El maletín Krauser K-Wing no se ajusta al soporte C-Bow.
El portador está diseñado de forma mucho más discreta que un portaequipajes lateral normal y por lo tanto no es adecuado para grandes cargas.
Carga recomendada: 5 kg por bolsa (por favor, tenga en cuenta las instrucciones de montaje, indicaciones específicas del vehículo, así como datos del fabricante de la motocicleta).
Se pueden combinar sin problemas con portaequipajes, barras de sisal o solares (ten en cuenta las instrucciones de instalación o las indicaciones específicas del vehículo).
Los ampliaciones del puente del equipaje pueden limitar el montaje de los bolsillos en el soporte.
Portaequipajes no necesita ABE o registro en los papeles.

desc2: Sumérgete en una experiencia visual y de rendimiento sin igual con el portátil gaming Medion Major 16 X1 MD62735, equipado con tecnología de vanguardia para gamers y creadores. Su pantalla QHD+ de 16 pulgadas y la poderosa GeForce RTX 5070 garantizan gráficos fluidos y realistas. ¡Eleva tus proyectos y juegos a un nuevo nivel! Los procesadores Intel Core Ultra para portátiles (Serie 2) ofrecen un desempeño de nivel entusiasta con experiencias de IA y menor consumo de energía en portátiles delgados con arquitectura híbrida de desempeño 3D de P-core, E-core e E-core de bajo consumo energético. Con más núcleos que mejoran el rendimiento de un solo hilo y de varios hilos, acelerador de NPU que ejecuta tareas de IA localmente, y la capacidad de llegar hasta los 36 TOPS gracias a las CPUs, GPUs y NPUs integradas, el procesador Intel Core Ultra 9 275HX es perfecto para entusiastas Gamers, creadores de contenido y profesionales. Conéctate a múltiples pantallas gracias a la compatibilidad independiente con Thunderbolt 4 e Thunderbolt 5, añade más almacenamiento, maximiza las configuraciones y disfruta de una conexión inalámbrica con Wi-Fi 6E (5 Gig) y Bluetooth 5.3. ¡Todo lo necesario para un alto desempeño en gaming, creación o trabajo! Gracias a su gran almacenamiento interno de 2TB SSD, podrás transferir tus datos en alta velocidad, y con 32GB de memoria RAM, los tiempos de carga se reducirán considerablemente. title: Celestron 94020 Dew Shield with Cover Cap, aluminium Dew Prevention, Fits 6” Schmidt Cassegrain Telescopes
description:
About this item
HELPS PREVENT DEW FORMATION ON THE SCHMIDT CORRECTOR LENS: Enhanced image quality, longer observation sessions, lens protection
RIGID BODY WITH A VELVET-LINED INTERIOR SURFACE: Reduces stray light for better image quality
PREVENTS OFF-AXIS GLARE FROM ENTERING THE OPTICAL SYSTEM: Improved vision and comfort
TWO ADJUSTABLE CLIPS: Easy installation and disassembly
CABLE MANAGEMENT AT THE BASE OF THE SHIELD: For using the Fastar/Hyperstar configuration or using in conjunction with the Celestron dew heater rings
desc2: This Aluminum Dew Shield with Cover Cap fits all 6” Celestron Schmidt-Cassegrain telescope tubes. It’s an essential accessory that protects the tube in the field. The dew shield reduces radiative cooling of the Schmidt corrector lens to the night sky, keeping the lens below the dew point longer and preventing dew from forming on the lens. The Aluminum Dew Shield also increases image contrast by blocking stray light from entering the telescope. Use the Aluminum Dew Shield on your 6” Schmidt Cassegrain telescope tube confidently, knowing it was created for your exact instrument.

title: RESTO Modern Wok Pan 28 cm, Wok, Frying Pan with High Rim - Non-Stick Coating - Ergonomic Handle with Hanging Loop and Anti-deformation Disc - Suitable for All Hobs Including Induction
description:
About this item
This wok pan combines traditional classic shapes with new modern technologies.
Comfortable ergonomic handle with hanging loop.
The pan base is reinforced with an anti-deformation disc.
This sauté pan is equipped with a modern induction base.
Optimal frying result thanks to even heat distribution.
desc2:
Antares Collection

The traditional wok pan has a convex bottom and high walls, but recently, flat bottom models that can be used on standard cooking surfaces have become equally popular. Our Antares frying pan is a perfect example of how old, traditional classic shapes can be adapted to new modern technologies. This allows you to cook popular Asian dishes at home. Take all the necessary ingredients: pasta, onion, rice and egg, prepare your culinary masterpiece and be sure that the Antares wok pan will leave a lasting impression on your guests.

In a wok, unlike a conventional pan, the heat is distributed more evenly due to the curved base. All ingredients are heated evenly and the cooking process is simple and fast, which a conventional frying pan cannot provide. If you want to impress others with Asian cuisine, try making something in this unique pan.

This wok pan combines traditional classic shapes with new modern technologies.
Comfortable ergonomic handle with hanging loop.
The pan base is reinforced with an anti-deformation disc.

Optimal frying result thanks to even heat distribution.
desc2:
Antares Collection

The traditional wok pan has a convex bottom and high walls, but recently, flat bottom models that can be used on standard cooking surfaces have become equally popular. Our Antares frying pan is a perfect example of how old, traditional classic shapes can be adapted to new modern technologies. This allows you to cook popular Asian dishes at home. Take all the necessary ingredients: pasta, onion, rice and egg, prepare your culinary masterpiece and be sure that the Antares wok pan will leave a lasting impression on your guests.

In a wok, unlike a conventional pan, the heat is distributed more evenly due to the curved base. All ingredients are heated evenly and the cooking process is simple and fast, which a conventional frying pan cannot provide. If you want to impress others with Asian cuisine, try making something in this unique pan.

desc2: Der Zeppelin LZ 126 war das erste Passagier-Luftschiff, das für Langstreckenflüge eingesetzt wurde. Für die Fahrt von Friedrichshafen nach New York im Jahre 1924 brauchte er nur 81 Stunden, damals ein absoluter Geschwindigkeitsrekord. Dieses große Ereignis würdigt die Uhrenserie LZ 126, die wie ihr Vorbild durch technische Raffinesse und stilvolle Eleganz überzeugt und mit der doppelten, zweifarbigen Tachymeterskala das Thema Geschwindigkeit zitiert.

MPS M42 Serie 60 - Sierras perforadoras para acero inoxidable, acero inoxidable, metal, acero, vigas de acero, perfiles abiertos gruesos y tubos de acero de resistencia media/diámetro

La sierra de corona se utiliza en combinación con un taladro eléctrico para cortar agujeros circulares a una profundidad limitada en diferentes materiales.

La sierra de corona genera un agujero preciso, por ejemplo, para pasacables de tubos, enchufes y cajas de dispositivos en diferentes materiales.
En este caso, solo se elimina poco material, ya que solo se crea un orificio de centrado y un corte de sierra circular en el material a mecanizar.

Las sierras de corona HSS bi-metal (de M42 bi-metal) están diseñadas para trabajar acero inoxidable, acero inoxidable, metal, acero, vigas de acero, perfiles abiertos gruesos,
perfiles cerrados gruesos y tubos de acero de resistencia media.

Otras características:
-Aleación con 8% de cobalto.
- Larga vida útil gracias a una mayor resistencia al calor.
- Profundidad de corte: 40 mm aprox.

desc2:
MPS M42 Series 60 Hole Saws for Stainless Steel, Stainless Steel, Metal, Steel, Steel Beams, Thick Open Profiles and Medium Strength/Diameter Steel Tubes

The hole saw is used in combination with an electric drill to cut circular holes to a limited depth in different materials.

The hole saw generates a precise hole, for example for cable grounds of pipes, sockets and device boxes in different materials.
In this case, only little material is removed, since only a centering hole and a circular saw cut are created in the material to be machined.

HSS bi-metal hole saws (M42 bi-metal) are designed to work stainless steel, stainless steel, metal, steel, steel beams, thick open profiles,
thick closed profiles and medium-strength steel tubes.

Other Features:
-Alloy with 8% cobalt.
- Long service life thanks to increased heat resistance.
- Cutting depth: approx. 40 mm.

desc2: Celestron revolutionize Dobson-style tabletop telescopes with the StarSense Explorer. This innovative telescope combines sky recognition technology with your smartphone to analyze and track celestial objects in real time. The app's intuitive interface and detailed tutorials make stargazing look like a personalized guided tour. Say goodbye to complicated star maps and imprecise planetary applications. With StarSense Explorer, you can locate objects easily, quickly and accurately. Its setup is very simple, and in a few minutes you will confidently travel the night sky. Simply place your smartphone in the StartSense stand, launch the app and perform a quick alignment. The app will generate a list of visible celestial objects depending on their location. The arrows will guide your telescope as you move it towards the selected object, and a green crosshair will indicate that you are ready to observe. With its 130mm parabolic-shaped primary mirror, this telescope collects lots of light for detailed views of celestial wonders such as Jupiter's moons, Saturn's rings or the Orion Nebula. Its stable Dobson desktop base provides a firm foundation, and is compact and lightweight for easy transportation. Azimuth and smooth latitude movement are guaranteed thanks to Teflon bearings, while its integrated altitude "braking" system allows tension adjustment. Tube rings and a dovetail bar make it easy to position for ergonomic observation, and an eyepiece rack will keep them always at hand. StarSense Explorer is compatible with iPhone 6 and later, and most Android devices manufactured from 2016 that have Android 7.1.2 or later.

title: Puig 21441O Clutch Lever Protector with Mirror Pro Gold
description:
This Puig product is an exercise in design and practicality as it manages to elegantly and compactly combine the lever guard with a mirror placed at the end of the handlebar
Made from a great aluminium block with black anodizing, it has a modern and sporty look; the anodizing of the end of the protector is available in several colours, so it is best matched with the latest sports naked on the market
With its installation, in addition to giving the motorcycle a more sporty and personalized look, it prevents accidental operation of the clutch or brake lever in the event of a collision with another vehicle, as well as adding additional protection
The mirror can be adjusted manually, quickly providing the best setting for each rider and can be easily repositioned in case it moves due to a small impact
Check the compatibility with your motorcycle in the Product Description section

description:

Realizzata in un ottimo blocco di alluminio con anodizzazione nera, ha un look moderno e sportivo; l'anodizzazione dell'estremità del protettore è disponibile in più colori, in modo da abbinarla al meglio alle ultime naked sportive in commercio

title: Trailer Axxle, through axle for bicycle trailers, in various sizes, high-quality stainless steel, connecting element for bicycles
description:
About this item
Quick and easy: the thru-axles allow easy and quick attachment to the bike. This saves valuable time and makes it easier to switch between different bicycles
Minimised vibrations: thanks to the direct connection, the axles minimise vibrations and shocks, which increases comfort for children and pets in the trailer and makes the ride more comfortable
Stability and safety: our TÜV tested axles meet DIN EN 15918:2017 I 6.15.2.1 to ensure safe use and a reliable driving experience
Easy to install: no special tools or professional know-how are required for mounting the thru-axles. The axles can be mounted without special expertise
UNIVERSAL COMPATIBILITY: The thru-axles are standardized, which ensures compatibility with different bicycle models and types. Thus, the axles are a real all-rounder
desc2: The safety of your children, pets and your luggage is our top priority. This high-quality thru-axle for bicycle trailers has been specially designed to improve stability and safety. Whether you're on short city trips or adventurous trips, our robust thru-axle ensures a reliable driving experience. Our TÜV tested axles have been tested to the highest requirements and comply with DIN EN 15918:2017 I 6.15.2.1. Product specifications: Compatibility: bicycles with 12 mm thru axle on the rear wheel. Installation: Easy to install without special tools. Diameter: 12 mm, colour: black, material: 7075-T6 aluminium/stainless steel, place of manufacture: Germany – made in Germany. Box contents: 1 x thru axle, 1 x spacer set (depending on the design), 1 x lock nut and washer. Details: If you are unsure which axle is the right one, please contact us. We are happy to advise you! Please read our assembly instructions carefully before installation.

desc2: Experience the perfect blend of comfort, protection, and performance with our Knitted Waterproof Gloves, engineered to keep your hands comfortable in cold, dry, or wet conditions during your cycling journeys. Seamless Comfort: We've designed these gloves with seamless construction, eliminating uncomfortable seams and pressure points, ensuring an unparalleled level of comfort for your hands. Waterproof Construction: The gloves feature a 3-layer construction with a waterproof membrane, providing excellent protection against cold rain and wind, all while maintaining exceptional dexterity. title: Puig 21994V Protezione Leva Frizione RAW con Contrappeso - Design Robusto e Adattabilità Universale, Verde
description:
About this item
Protezione leva frizione RAW Puig 21994V, progettata per l’uso in pista, con corpo centrale in alluminio anodizzato e punta in poliammide resistente, ideale per evitare danni da contatti accidentali.
Compatibile con manubri di diametro interno da 13 a 18 mm, senza necessità di adattatori per la maggior parte dei modelli, con adattatori specifici disponibili per le moto che ne hanno bisogno.
Include il contrappeso per il lato sinistro, con possibilità di acquistare un contrappeso aggiuntivo per il lato destro, garantendo un’estetica uniforme e componenti perfettamente abbinati.
Progettato esclusivamente per leve Puig; la compatibilità con tutte le leve originali, contrappesi o specchietti non è garantita.
Verifica le moto compatibili con questo prodotto nel file PDF allegato.
desc2: La protezione leva frizione RAW Puig 21994V in colore verde è la soluzione ideale per chi cerca sicurezza e funzionalità sia su pista che su strada. Progettata per prevenire contatti accidentali che potrebbero azionare la frizione o i freni, questa protezione combina un corpo centrale lavorato in alluminio anodizzato con una punta in poliammide quasi indistruttibile, garantendo massima resistenza e durata. Compatibile con manubri di diametro interno tra 13 e 18 mm, l’installazione è semplice e non richiede adattatori specifici per la maggior parte dei modelli. Tuttavia, adattatori specifici sono disponibili per i modelli che ne necessitano. Questa protezione include il contrappeso per il lato sinistro, con l’opzione di acquistare un contrappeso aggiuntivo per il lato destro, permettendo un design uniforme e coerente per la tua moto. Progettata specificamente per leve Puig, non si garantisce la compatibilità con leve originali, contrappesi o specchietti a contrappeso. La referenza 21993N deve essere acquistata per la protezione e, se si desidera uniformità su entrambi i lati, sono necessarie due referenze in totale. Perfetta per chi cerca funzionalità ed estetica, la protezione RAW è lavorata con precisione e anodizzata in colori che si adattano allo stile di ogni motocicletta.

About this item
Hy-Wood Construction A completely unique club head design that combines the control of a hybrid with the spacing of a fairway wood, its head size and shape along with its shaft length fall directly between fairway woods and hybrids. MainFrame XL Face MainFrame XL Face Technology uses a variable thickness pattern that maximizes flexibility on impact to increase distance. It also positions the weight low and low in the club head for added forgiveness and consistency.

XL Head Design An improved XL head design with low and low weighting, players can enjoy long, high-start ball flight with plenty of forgiveness.

title: COMPRESSPORT R2 3.0 Calf Sleeves - AW25
description:
About this item
Quick-Drying Fabric - To keep you feeling dry and comfortable during activity. Perfect for summer months.
K-Protect Knee Tab - Reduces shocks and discomfort around the knee.
Targeted Waffle Knit Zones - Promote microcirculation, reducing inflammation as well as stomach problems over long distance runs.
360-Degree Compression - High-level muscle support to the calves, decreasing the risk of injury and cramps.
Textured Fibular Stripes - Stimulate proprioceptors, increasing grip and reducing the chance of sprained ankles for improved balance and stability.
desc2: Compressport R2 3.0 Calf Sleeves The evolution of Compressport's iconic R2v2 compression calf-sleeves, increasing stability and reducing shock - wherever you're running. Building on Compressport's most iconic product, the updated R2 3.0 takes all the features that made the R2v2 so well respected and combines them with new updated features to increase stability. The R2 3.0 has the same exclusive seamless multi-gradual compression, quick-drying fabric and purposely designed K-Protect knee tab. These features are designed to reduce shock and have been combined with more revolutionary details. New Fibular Stripes activate proprioception to increase balance and stability helping reduce the risk of sprains on the trail. Targeted horizontal waffle knit areas promote microcirculation and lymphatic flow to prevent shin splints and inflammation from occurring. After learning of a recent scientific report which showed that compression sleeves can help reduce stomach problems after strenuous activity, Compressport honed these waffle knit zones to further promote blood flow around the body and reduce intestinal damage. In short, no more stomach-cramp-induced DNFs. Whether you're jogging around the park or halfway through the Barkley Marathons, the R2 3.0 will support you in going the extra mile. Lastly, reflective logos feature on the sleeves for improved visibility in low-light conditions.

desc2: Compressport Pro Racing v4.0 Trail Socks High-tech trail running socks that protect, absorb shocks and support your feet during your toughest off-road challenges. The Pro Racing Socks from Compressport support your feet in many different ways with new and improved features for the 4th generation. The socks provide Achilles protection thanks to the cushioning effect of the 3D.Dots at the rear of the sock, and work to protect the Achilles tendon from friction and pressure. These 3D.Dots are also on the inner part of the malleolus to help prevent shocks. The massaging acupressure within the sock is designed to activate blood circulation by multipoint massaging of the sole area, whilst arch support is located in the arch of the foot for venous return and recovery. A 360° slight compression band around the arch support prevent the socks from turning or sliding down during movement, for minimal distractions. Most importantly, it stimulates venous return delivering more tonicity to your stride. The socks also adhere to your foot's anatomy and help to maintain your performance. The sock has been designed to include striped vented zones around the feet for total ventilation, allowing cool air to permeate and hot air to escape, helping to prevent an intolerable heat build-up. Combined with its fast-drying fibres, the sock drys very quickly so you avoid wet feet, and the 3D.Dots do not retain water and instead help to facilitate its discharge for dry feet at all times. Seamless and elastic-free, the sock does not create unnecessary irritation or pressure, so in the ergonomic toe box, the forefoot can lie comfortably and the toe box has been made wider than its previous version for improved proprioception. The fabric features reinforcements in key areas to protect the ankle, toes and nails from the rough demands of trail running and increase the overall durability of the sock.

title: EVVO Ceiling Fan with Rechargeable Blades and Light, Ø107cm, 3 Blades, DC 40W Motor, 6 Speeds, Timer up to 4h, Winter-Summer Function, IP44 Protection (Black)
description:
About this item
The design of the ceiling fan seeks to combine elegant lighting without compromising the effectiveness in air circulation. Its retractable blades allow you to hide them according to your preference, a unique feature compared to other models of fans.
The ceiling fan comes with a sleek and minimalist ceiling lamp that provides ample luminosity. With options of 3 different shades (warm, neutral and cool) and 6 operating speeds, you can adjust it to perfectly suit your lighting and ventilation needs.
With a diameter of 42 inches (107 cm) when the blades are unfolded, this fan is ideal for any space. Its remote control allows you to manage all functions conveniently and easily.
The fan with invisible blades features an innovative twist reversing system that makes it versatile for all seasons of the year. In summer, it provides a refreshing breeze, while in winter it helps to distribute the warm air that collects at the top of the room, thus becoming an ideal ally for your heating system.
This fan delivers exceptional 40W power, with a high-performance copper motor that ensures increased airflow and an unmatched cool feeling, all with maximum reliability and durability. In addition, its functionality is enhanced by a convenient timer, which allows you to select between several options of uninterrupted operation (1, 2, or 4 hours), after which the fan will automatically turn off, providing a more convenient and efficient use experience.

Say goodbye to sweaty helmets and hello to a fresh and breathable riding experience.
Most importantly, the Thousand Kids Helmet is safety certified for biking, roller skating, and skateboarding, ensuring that your child is protected no matter what wheels they ride. With the peace of mind that comes from knowing your child is wearing a helmet that meets CSPC, ASTM, and CE safety standards, you can relax and enjoy watching them explore and play with confidence.
Give your child the gift of safety, style, and self-expression with the Thousand Kids Helmet from the Jr Collection. With its customizable design, adjustable fit, active ventilation, and safety certifications, this helmet is the perfect choice for young riders who want to stay safe and look cool while they play.

description:
Visit a multitude of exotic planets through trapping-filled levels that will test your skills to the limit. With the superhuman abilities of cobra, you'll have to run, jump and climb relentlessly, and make sure you use every means at your fingertips to take down your enemies.
Master iconic cobra weapons, such as the stunning psychogun and colt python 77, to destroy opponents who step on your heels, as well as their famous gadgets like the cigar and hook. You will need your entire arsenal to defeat the powerful bosses who stand in your way.
Explore the story mode by choosing from 3 difficulty levels, allowing veterans of the genre to face a true test worthy of their skills, while those looking for a minor challenge can enjoy the story. You can also try to escape your enemies in a 2-player co-op mode.
Immerse yourself in this amazing world of space opera as you embark on your adventure as a fearsome and charismatic hero. Throughout this epic journey, you'll come across picturesque characters like the royal sisters and the terrifying crystal bowie, the cobra nemesis.
Space adventure cobra - the awakening is the first cobra video game adaptation on modern platforms. covers the first 12 episodes of the famous anime series, staying true to her spirit with the moments of bravery and humor that made her so special.

desc2:
Double sound enjoyment.
CMF Buds 2 Plus are designed for an enhanced listening experience. Hi-Res LDAC certified sound combined with an Audiodo hearing test and custom sound correction ensures a detailed sound that's tailored to your hearing.

Stay in your world.
Avoid distractions with Hybrid ANC and 5400Hz noise cancellation. Smart Adaptive Mode adjusts in real time for optimal noise reduction. Activate Adaptive in the Nothing X app for fine tuning. The mode also compensates for sound loss through the ear canal so you can immerse yourself in your music.

Hear every detail
Experience every sound the way it should sound. The 12mm LCD driver combined with LDAC technology and Hi-Res Wireless Audio certification delivers dynamic, rich sound with deep, powerful bass and finely nuanced treble. High-purity copper wires and N52 magnets ensure superior sound clarity - a studio experience right in your ears.

Sound that adapts to your needs
Personal Sound adjusts the sound exactly to your listening profile for a completely personalized listening experience. Powered by Audiodo, the function performs a precise listening test with pure tones to analyze your sensitivity at different frequencies and dynamically align the sound for greater clarity and balance.

Immerse yourself in the sound
CMF Buds 2 Plus feature spatial audio effect with Head-Related Transfer Function (HRTF) technology to create an immersive, three-dimensional listening experience. Whether you're watching a movie, playing or deep in your playlist, every sound moves with you.

A battery that keeps up
Up to 14 hours of playback on a single charge, expandable to 61.5 hours with case (AAC, ANC off). A short 10-minute charge allows 8.5 hours of music playback and keeps you connected longer.

First-class and elegant.
The smooth, soft surface and sandblasted metal elements provide a classy feel. For comfortable wearing comfort that naturally adapts to the ear¹¹. A design that combines style and function.

Clear conversations in any environment
CMF Buds 2 Plus provide crystal clear calls with 6 HD microphones, Clear Voice Technology 3.0 and advanced noise cancelling algorithms. Trained with millions of real ambient sounds, the technology adapts to busy roads and traffic hubs. Wind Noise Reduction 3.0 also improves clarity in windy conditions.

Long lasting protection
IP55 protection for even better durability. Tackles intense workouts, outdoor adventures and unpredictable weather conditions with ease. Keep focus and stay connected anywhere, anytime.

Even more features in the Nothing X app
Adjust the EQ, Ultra Bass and ANC settings with the Nothing X app8. Enable low-lag mode for gaming and use ChatGPT for intelligent voice interactions. Seamless integration with all Nothing devices.

title: Daemon X Machina: Titanic Scion - Xbox
description:
About this item
A titanic evolution - Daemon X Machina's intense armored action debuts on a new generation of platforms, and it does so with an epic sci-fi adventure, beginner friendly gameplay and a wider stage that won't leave fans indifferent.
Create a better version of you - Now that the arsenal is a versatile armored suit, you can fully customize its look and gear, and also have the ability to manufacture or recover new items.
Make a difference in company - Thanks to co-op multiplayer mode, you'll never fight alone. Join your friends online to tackle the amazing story and fight bosses together.
BEAUTIFUL AND LETHAL - Explore an alien planet with your arsenal as you battle mechanical and organic enemies. Ride the immense open world on foot, fly through the sky, or when all else fails, ride through plains, swamps, mountains and more.

desc2:
Hundreds of years after the battle for the reddish soils of Early Earth, humans have colonized the blue planet. The Outers (people born with special abilities to have exposed themselves to Femto, a peculiar source of energy) began to be outraged by the contempt they suffered at the hands of humanity on this new and dangerous planet. They took control of The Garden, orbital defense satellites from which they rule the planet as a military power called Sovereign Axiom. As humans on the planet's surface struggle to survive the elements and a race of half-organic half-mechanical creatures known as Immortals, a resistance group, The Reclaimers, appears to stand up against the brutal dominance of the Axiom. When an Outer soldier crashes into the desert outside humanity's greatest settlement, hope arises that he will become the key to turning the tables of the last human revolution.

Marvelous First Studio presents an action-packed new installment of the Daemon X Machina saga. Fly into battle in your custom arsenal and perform a wide variety of attacks tailored to your playing style. Feel the thrill of fast-paced combat as you explore a deadly and dangerous open world by land or air. After killing your enemies, collect their weapons and equipment, and improve your skills to have more options on the battlefield. Get ready for a dark sci-fi story where you must face titanic battles against solo bosses or with up to two friends online. New Daemon X Machina players and veterans alike can enjoy an incredible adventure.

Daemon X Machina: Titanic Scion , created and produced by Kenichiro Tsukuda and featuring the incredible mechanical designs of Shoji Kawamori, is a twist on the franchise. Join The Reclaimers in their fight against Axiom. The battle for the liberation of humanity is beginning now!

MAIN FEATURES

A titanic evolution - Daemon X Machina's intense armored action debuts on a new generation of platforms, and it does so with an epic sci-fi adventure, beginner friendly gameplay and a wider stage that won't leave fans indifferent.

Create a better version of you - Now that the arsenal is a versatile armored suit, you can fully customize its look and gear, and also have the ability to manufacture or recover new items.

Make a difference in company - Thanks to co-op multiplayer mode, you'll never fight alone. Join your friends online to tackle the amazing story and fight bosses together.

BEAUTIFUL AND LETHAL - Explore an alien planet with your arsenal as you battle mechanical and organic enemies. Ride the immense open world on foot, fly through the sky, or when all else fails, ride through plains, swamps, mountains and more.

title: Continental Magnotal Tubeless Ready Mountain Bike Tyre, 1 Piece, Quick Grip on Mixed and Loose Terrain, E25 Electric Bike Folding
description:
About this item
RELIABLE ALL ROUNDER: Dominate every ride with the ultra-versatile Magnotal mountain bike tire, the go-to solution for aggressive down-country, all-mountain and trail use - with E25 eBike rating for added wear resistance and puncture protection.
FAST, GRIP & HEAVY DUTY With our innovative grip compound and trail housing, this tire provides balanced traction and rolling resistance, backed by a lightweight yet durable single-layer carcass construction perfect for trail, gravel and cross country use.
TAKE ON ANY TERRAIN: Designed for loose, mixed, muddy or hard soils, the Magnotal's newly designed tread system provides enhanced traction, balance, and cornering stability for everything from messy spin cycle climbs to fast rain descents.
TUBELESS READY This bike tire is tubeless and snagless compatible, giving you more control over your setup; blends seamlessly with our self-repairing Conti Revo Sealant for added protection and comfort when riding with lower air pressure.
SPECIFICATIONS Size: 27.5" x 2.4" ISO/ETRTO Size: 60-584 Max Tire Pressure: 50 PSI / 3.45 Bar Weight: 805g TR Tubeless Ready: Compatible with Conti Revo Sealant or Inflatable Tyre Tube; E25 E-Bike Rated; Tread & Sidewall Flat Protection
desc2: The Continental Magnotal mountain bike tyre is the ultimate all-rounder for aggressive down-country, all-mountain and trail riding. Built to handle everything from hard or loose ground to wet, muddy terrain, this versatile tire combines an innovative grip blend with a lightweight yet durable trail housing for an excellent balance of relentless traction and moderate rolling resistance. The E25 electric bike rating construction provides enhanced puncture protection and durability whether you're traversing muddy climbs or tearing soft dirt descents. The revised mid tread lug pattern and increased cavity volume optimize traction in mixed terrain, while the knobs of the transition area provide stable support through technical sections, and the reinforced shoulder studs with additional slats provide secure cornering grip in all conditions. Tubeless-ready and hookless compatible, seamlessly matches our Conti Revo Sealant for fewer flats and the ability to run lower pressures. Plus, its foldable design fits perfectly into your bike backpack alongside essential accessories such as your repair kit, tyre levers, replacement tubes and CO2 cartridges. No matter what terrain, dominate every ride with the Magnotal.

description:
About this item
FRAME MODULAR CHASSIS SYSTEM - The revolutionary FRAME system gives new meaning to the word customization. The revolutionary FRAME modular chassis system redefines customization. desc2: Pair of waterproof side bags with MONOKEY fixing system, 25+25 lt The GRT720B Canyon side bags are designed for lovers of off-road routes who do not want to give up convenience and safety in the transport of their luggage, even when travelling on rough terrain. desc2: Camiseta Leatt Moto 4.5 X-Flow: Máxima ventilación y confort para climas extremos Cuando el calor aprieta y la exigencia del terreno no da tregua, la camiseta Leatt Moto 4.5 X-Flow es tu mejor aliada. Diseñada para ofrecer una ventilación imbatible gracias a su tejido X-Flow ultratranspirable, esta camiseta permite rendir al máximo sin sobrecalentamientos, incluso en las condiciones más duras. Beneficios y uso recomendado de la camiseta Moto 4.5 X-Flow Perfecta para motocross, enduro o trail en climas cálidos, esta camiseta ha sido creada para los riders que priorizan la frescura, la ligereza y la libertad de movimiento. Su combinación de tecnología MoistureCool y malla abierta permite mantener el cuerpo seco y ventilado durante toda la ruta. * Tejido X-Flow Mesh: malla ultratranspirable que favorece un flujo de aire constante y eficiente. * Tecnología MoistureCool: gestiona la humedad para mantenerte seco y fresco durante más tiempo. * Corte clásico refinado: permite el uso con o sin protecciones, adaptándose a cada estilo de pilotaje. * Costuras Overlock: minimizan las rozaduras y mejoran la comodidad general. * Cuello técnico compatible con collarín: diseño Brace Ready para integración con protecciones Leatt. Disponible en tallas S a 3XL La camiseta Leatt Moto 4.5 X-Flow está hecha para los que no se detienen ni cuando el calor es extremo. Disfruta de la máxima transpirabilidad, sin renunciar a la comodidad ni al estilo. Una prenda técnica que te acompaña en cada aventura off-road.

desc2: Leatt Moto 5.5 Ultraweld T-Shirt: Elite Performance Designed for motocross riders who demand the utmost, the Leatt Moto 5.5 Ultraweld Jersey exceeds any expectation in comfort, lightness and textile technology applied to motocross and enduro. Available in sizes S to 3XL Master any stroke with the safety and comfort that only Leatt can offer. The Moto 5.5 Ultraweld is not just a t-shirt, it is technology applied to high-level riding. Put it on, feel control and take your performance to the next level.

desc2: Leatt Moto 4.5 Junior T-Shirt: Comfort and ventilation for young riders The Leatt Moto 4.5 Junior Jersey has been designed to offer younger riders the same level of performance and comfort as adult models. The optimised classic cut allows you to wear comfortably with or without protections, adapting to the body without restriction. The 3D Stretch Mesh fabric combined with X-Flow side panels ensures superior ventilation and excellent moisture management thanks to MoistureCool technology. This allows you to keep the body cool and dry, even in the most intense days. Benefits and recommended use Perfect for motocross, enduro or weekend outings, the Moto 4.5 Junior stands out for its comfort, breathability and durability. Ideal for young riders looking to progress with a technical and durable kit with the Leatt seal of quality. Main features * Classic youth cut: adapted to the body of young riders, compatible with protections. * 3D Stretch Mesh: soft to the touch, stretchy and snag resistant. * X-Flow panels: extreme ventilation on the sides to control body heat. * MoistureCool fabric: wicks away moisture and keeps skin dry and comfortable. * Low profile collar - technical and compatible with Leatt collars. * Elastic cuffs: comfortable fit that doesn't oppress. * Back silicone band: keeps the shirt firmly attached to the trousers. * Sustainability: PFAS free (PFC), plastic-free packaging and OekoTex and Reach certifications. * Sizes: Junior S - XL. With the Leatt Moto 4.5 Junior T-shirt, young riders will enjoy the maximum freedom of movement, freshness and style that characterizes the Leatt range. A technical garment designed to grow with them in every adventure on the bike.

desc2: Compressport ArmForce Ultralight Arm Sleeves Thanks to a new generation of compression tubes, the Armforce Ultralight targets compression on strategic arm muscles to the millimetre. Blood flow is stimulated, enabling the muscles to get even more oxygen thus, guarding against injury and cramps. The muscles are supported for strength and better performance on longer distances. Ultra-extensible, the fibre is also more breathable for maximum comfort. A lighter weave is used at the elbow to allow exceptional freedom of movement whilst providing extra ventilation so that you can focus on your training. The construction wicks sweat as it's produced. Once wicked, the fabric transfers the sweat to the outer layers where it can be easily evaporated. No more uncomfortable, heavy, damp clothing that irritates and does not dry. Finishing the Arm Sleeves is the brand's signature 3D.Dots are built into the forearms to enhance blood circulation, although they may also double up as excellent sweatbands when intensity builds. The sleeves are quick to pull on and remove making them convenient for cycling, running and endurance sports, saving you the added weight of an extra layer. Department ‏ : ‎ Hombre
desc2:
Las GARMONT Pinnacle Evo GTX son unas botas de montaña robustas y potentes para hombre, especialmente diseñadas para excursiones exigentes en terrenos alpinos. La membrana impermeable Gore-Tex Performance Comfort mantiene los pies secos y al mismo tiempo garantiza una transpirabilidad óptima, perfecta para condiciones climáticas cambiantes.

La piel Perwanger de alta calidad es extremadamente resistente a la abrasión y ofrece la máxima protección contra piedras y escombros junto con los dedos y el talón reforzados. La suela Vibram garantiza el mejor agarre en roca, nieve, barro y terrenos irregulares. La entresuela de EVA amortiguadora reduce el estrés en las articulaciones y proporciona una gran comodidad incluso en etapas largas.

Gracias al eje alto, el Pinnacle Evo GTX ofrece una excelente estabilidad y apoyo. Los cordones precisos de dos zonas permiten una adaptación individual al pie para un agarre óptimo. Con solo aprox. 750 g por zapato (talla 42), esta bota de montaña combina estabilidad con un peso moderado, ideal para escaladores que viajan en condiciones exigentes.

title: SIGMA Aura 50 LED Bicycle Light with 50 LUX and USB-C | StVZO Approved Front Light with 2 Light Modes & Automatic Light Adjustment | Long Battery Life
description:
About this item
Permanent burner: the Aura 50 has two light modes. In high mode, it reliably lights up the way for up to 9 hours, in ECO mode even up to 28 hours! Thanks to the memory function, the AURA 50 lights up as it was switched off the next time it was switched on.
CLEVER – The front light thinks with: In auto mode, an integrated brightness sensor automatically regulates the light intensity – depending on the ambient light. This ensures optimal lighting and the battery is used particularly efficiently.
Rechargeable: the Aura 50 has an integrated rechargeable battery. Via USB-C the front light can be fully charged in 3 hours. This saves money and protects the environment. A short press on the button is enough, and the three-stage LED indicator shows the current battery level. Even when charging, cyclists can keep track of progress thanks to the display.
Power on protection: the light is switched on with a double click and switched off again by pressing the button for a long time. This function prevents accidental activation, such as in the school bag or backpack.
Easy to install – thanks to the 360° adjustable silicone holder, the Aura 50 is attached to the handlebars without tools in seconds. It can be aligned horizontally and vertically as needed. So that the light can be stored even faster and more space-saving, it is equipped with a "quick release" - so you can remove it while the holder remains firmly on the wheel.
Weatherproof – the Aura 50 likes to take on all cycling adventures. It is splash-proof according to IP44 - ideal for all weather conditions in city traffic.
Visibility – The side light guide is not only an optical highlight. The two additional LEDs ensure significantly higher lateral visibility.
Sustainable - The front light meets the requirements of the EU battery regulation. The screwed housing allows the professional replacement of the battery by authorised bodies - for more sustainability and safety.

title: Bugaboo Thermolite Performance coprigambe
description:
About this item
Isolamento termico innovativo: alternativa vegana ad alte prestazioni realizzata con risorse riciclate al 100% mantiene il bambino caldo, accogliente e protetto in condizioni climatiche invernali estreme.
Inserto rimovibile per l'uso tutto l'anno: aggiungi l'inserto isolante THERMOLITE nelle giornate fredde per un maggiore calore o rimuovilo in condizioni climatiche più miti per un comfort traspirante.
Morbida fodera in pile e cappuccio regolabile: l'interno in pile felpato e il cappuccio adattabile offrono comfort tutto il giorno e una vestibilità aderente che cresce con il tuo bambino.
Idrorepellente e resistente allo sporco: il guscio esterno resistente con cerniere impermeabili protegge da pioggia e neve, mentre uno scudo integrato mantiene l'interno pulito.

Para los días de sol, disfruta de bermudas, shorts, vestidos, bañadores y bikinis, perfectos para la playa y el mar. La línea surfera de Hurley destaca por su tecnología técnica y diseños auténticos que reflejan la pasión por la libertad y el movimiento.

Country of origin ‏ : ‎ Spain
Department ‏ : ‎ Men's
desc2:
Our Hi-Tec FIGARO LOW WP is a waterproof barefoot hiking shoe, developed to offer freedom of movement, stability and protection on changing routes. Its low-profile design, wide toe and flexible sole allows for a more natural step, strengthening the foot and improving the connection to the terrain.

The cut combines synthetic nubuck and water-repellent nylon, reinforced with a waterproof and breathable Dri-Tec membrane that protects against water and promotes internal ventilation. The Ghillie lacing system with double eyelet at the ankle enhances support on technical walks, while the moisture-wicking EVA foam insole and interior padding ensure lasting comfort.

It also incorporates a rear stabilizer and thermoplastic shank that reinforce the structure of the shoe, plus a grippy rubber outsole for reliable traction on wet or stony trails. Available in men's and women's versions, our FIGARO LOW WP model is ideal for those looking for a technical and resistant shoe, without giving up the natural footprint.

title: COLORBABY Bontempi - Tastiera musicale 61 tasti, 84,5 x 29 x 8,2 cm, leggio, 200 suoni, 200 ritmi, 60 demo, 3 livelli di apprendimento, cavo USB, pianoforti digitali, organo elettronico per bambini
description:
About this item

Design: tastiera a 61 tasti misura 84,5 x 29 x 8,2 cm, con supporto e display digitale a 3 cifre. Incorpora jack per cuffie (n/incluso), presa per microfono a condensatore (n/ incluso), presa per cavo USB tipo C (incluso), presa USB tramite flash drive e presa per sorgente musicale esterna (lettore MP3, smartphone, ecc.)
Funzioni: pulsanti on/off, registrazione e riproduzione, controllo del volume e del tempo, comandi MP3, 3 livelli di apprendimento (OKON, Follow e Ensemble), trasposer, chiave drum, accordi facili (Easy/Classic chord), Fill-in, Sync e Split, metronomo, spegnimento automatico e selettore di funzioni, suoni, demo, ritmi. Funziona con 6 batterie AA o con alimentatore esterno

Valori: strumento educativo che favorisce l'apprendimento, migliora la creatività e sviluppa la memoria
› See more product details
desc2:
Product description

Tocca, impara e divertiti con la tastiera elettronica Bontempi! Che cos'è? Scopri quanto è divertente imparare la musica con questa originale tastiera portatile per bambini di Bontempi! Con i suoi 61 tasti, il supporto integrato e un'ampia varietà di suoni, ritmi e melodie, i più piccoli potranno iniziare nel mondo musicale mentre lo passano in grande. Uno strumento completo, intuitivo e ricco di possibilità che trasforma l'apprendimento musicale in un'esperienza emozionante fin dal primo giorno! Contenuto della confezione: La tastiera per bambini include 200 suoni, 200 ritmi, 60 brani preregistrati, 5 suoni di basso per accompagnamento, polifonia a 8 note, 8 suoni di percussione ed effetto sustain e vibrato. Consente di registrare e ascoltare le proprie composizioni, selezionare l'opzione di accordi facili, toccare con 1, 2 o 3 dita, e controllare sia il volume che il tempo. Incorpora 3 funzioni di apprendimento (OKON, follow e ensemble) per suonare la melodia di una delle canzoni demo e altre funzioni avanzate come metronomo (per attivare o disattivare il tempo), fill-in (per introdurre una variazione ritmica della batteria), split (per dividere la tastiera in due sezioni: una parte per l'accompagnamento e una per la melodia), trasposer (per cambiare la tonalità), chiave drum (per attivare o disattivare gli strumenti a percussione) e sync (per avviare il ritmo e l'accompagnamento una volta composto l'accordo). Inoltre, include display digitale a 3 cifre per visualizzare le funzioni, presa per microfono a condensatore (non inclusa), presa per cuffie (non inclusa), presa USB per flash drive, presa per sorgente musicale esterna (lettore MP3, smartphone, ecc.) che consente di riprodurre i tuoi brani MP3 preferiti. Cosa imparano? Le tastiere musicali sono un ottimo strumento di apprendimento, in quanto richiedono una corretta lettura di note o accordi per riprodurre la melodia desiderata. Inoltre, con l'opzione di registrazione e riproduzione, i bambini possono comporre le proprie canzoni, il che migliora notevolmente la loro creatività. Ma non è tutto, per eseguire correttamente le canzoni, devono memorizzare le note, il che rappresenta una grande stimolazione per la memoria. Cosa dovresti sapere? Questo pianoforte elettronico per bambini è consigliato dai 3 anni in su e dispone di spegnimento automatico. Può funzionare con 6 batterie AA (non incluse) o tramite un alimentatore con adattatore di rete (non incluso) o tramite cavo USB di tipo C (incluso). Include manuale di istruzioni con spartiti musicali e il packaging ha una maniglia per trasportare la tastiera comodamente ovunque. Il regalo perfetto per i futuri artisti

Funzioni: pulsanti on/off, start/stop, registrazione e riproduzione, controllo del volume e del tempo, accordi facili, funzione di apprendimento (seguito), metronomo, trasposer, singolo, chiave drum, split e selettore di funzioni, suoni, canzoni e ritmi. desc2:
Product description

Porta il musicista dentro con questa tastiera portatile Bontempi! Che cos'è? Questa tastiera elettronica a 54 tasti Bontempi è lo strumento perfetto per imparare a suonare il pianoforte e divertirti allo stesso tempo. Grazie al leggio e alle gambe in metallo regolabili in altezza, puoi montare facilmente e rapidamente questo pianoforte per bambini nella tua stanza. Siediti su una sedia di fronte a lui e pratica comodamente ogni volta che ne hai voglia! Contenuto della confezione: La tastiera pianoforte per bambini include 100 suoni, 100 ritmi, 60 brani preregistrati e una polifonia fino a 8 note simultanee. Consente di registrare e riprodurre le proprie composizioni, selezionare l'opzione di accordi facili, toccare con 1, 2 o 3 dita, e regolare sia il volume che il tempo. Incorpora la funzione di apprendimento Follow, che consente di seguire una melodia preregistrata guidandoti dalle luci LED che si illuminano sulla tastiera. Inoltre, ha effetto sustain (per prolungare il suono) e altre funzioni avanzate come metronomo (per attivare o disattivare il tempo), trasposer (per cambiare la tonalità), singolo (per attivare la composizione degli accordi), key drum (per attivare o disattivare gli strumenti a percussione) e split (per dividere la tastiera in due sezioni: una parte per l'accompagnamento e una per la melodia). Dispone anche di display digitale, ingresso USB Type-C (cavo incluso), presa per alimentatore di rete (non incluso), presa per cuffie (non incluse), ingresso AUX per sorgente musicale esterna (lettore MP3 o smartphone) e connessione per microfono a condensatore (non incluso). Cosa imparano? Le tastiere musicali sono un ottimo strumento di apprendimento, in quanto richiedono una corretta lettura di note o accordi per ottenere la melodia desiderata. Inoltre, con l'opzione di registrazione e riproduzione, i bambini possono comporre le proprie canzoni, il che migliora notevolmente la loro creatività. Ma non è tutto, per eseguire correttamente le canzoni, devono memorizzare le note, il che rappresenta una grande stimolazione per la memoria. Cosa dovresti sapere? Questo pianoforte elettronico è consigliato dai 3 anni in su e funziona con 4 batterie AA (non incluse) o con adattatore di rete (non incluso) o con cavo USB di tipo C (incluso) per essere collegato a una power bank, PC, caricabatterie telefonico, ecc. (non incluso). Include manuale di istruzioni con tre spartiti musicali e la confezione dispone di maniglia per trasportare comodamente la tastiera. Il regalo perfetto per ragazzi e ragazze amanti della musica!

Diseñada para los amantes del deporte, el surf, el skate y la vida outdoors, ofrece prendas ideales para el verano y el invierno. Descubre una amplia variedad de productos como camiseta de manga corta o manga larga, tirantes, polo, camisa, t shirt, sudaderas, chaquetas, forros polares, gorros y gorras. Para los días de sol, disfruta de bermudas, shorts, vestidos, bañadores y bikinis, perfectos para la playa y el mar. También cuenta con pantalones técnicos y ropa transpirable ideal para la montaña y hacer snowboard. La línea surfera de Hurley destaca por su tecnología técnica y diseños auténticos que reflejan la pasión por la libertad y el movimiento.
